{"word":"G176 - ἀκατάγνωστος - akatágnōstos - ak-at-ag'-noce-tos - That cannot be condemned","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκατάγνωστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">akatágnōstos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak-at-ag'-noce-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">That cannot be condemned</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றம் பிடிக்கப்படாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"that cannot be condemned, not to be censured"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2607 - καταγινώσκω - kataginṓskō - kat-ag-in-o'-sko/2607\">G2607</a>; <i>unblamable:</i> - that cannot be condemned.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1097/1097\">G1097</a>, <a href=\"#/G1106/1106\">G1106</a>, <a href=\"#/G1107/1107\">G1107</a>, <a href=\"#/G1108/1108\">G1108</a>, <a href=\"#/G1110/1110\">G1110</a>, <a href=\"#/G176/176\">G176</a>, <a href=\"#/G1921/1921\">G1921</a>, <a href=\"#/G1922/1922\">G1922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2607/2607\">G2607</a>, <a href=\"#/G4267/4267\">G4267</a>, <a href=\"#/G4268/4268\">G4268</a>, <a href=\"#/G4774/4774\">G4774</a>"}]}